		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about sports that involve <a href="/wiki/Violence" title="Violence">violence</a> for <a href="/wiki/Entertainment" title="Entertainment">entertainment</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Bloodsport_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Bloodsport (disambiguation)">Bloodsport (disambiguation)</a>. For the similarly named blood effect, see <a href="/wiki/Blood_spurt" class="mw-redirect" title="Blood spurt">blood spurt</a>.</div>
