<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:282px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg/280px-Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg" decoding="async" width="280" height="212" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg/420px-Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg/560px-Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg 2x" data-file-width="768" data-file-height="581" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Brooklyn_Museum_-_Ram_Fight_One_of_274_Vintage_Photographs.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Before a ram fight, <a href="/wiki/Iran" title="Iran">Iran</a>, 1876-1925. <i>One of 274 Vintage Photographs</i>. <a href="/wiki/Brooklyn_Museum" title="Brooklyn Museum">Brooklyn Museum</a>.</div></div></div>
